text: Morong may refer to: *Thomas Morong (1827-1894), botanist * Morong, Bataan, a municipality in the Philippines * Morong, Rizal, a municipality in the Philippines * Distrito de Morong (Province of Morong), now a part of the province of Rizal * Morong, a sub-village of Umalsat, Tehsil Yasin, Ghizer District, Pakistan * Morong, Guzhang (默戎镇), a town of Guzhang County, Hunan, China.
